lead_paragraph: Masahiro Tanaka pitched four innings, allowing seven hits but just one run, and a split squad of New York Yankees led the Philadelphia Phillies 7-1 Tuesday when the game was rained out.

headline.print_headline: Tanaka Pitches 4 Innings, Yankees and Phillies Rained Out
